name: SuNdRoP
description: Loved working with Nneka. We shot this in East Orange, New Jersey. We did this in the spur of the moment. Location was the roof of her apartment. Minimalism is what I see in this photo. The reason why I chose this one is because I feel that theres so little but so much. The photo shows this sleek emotion that the viewer can perceive in different ways.The essence of the model almost jumps out the picture. This photo was taken on a Nikon D610 / 50mm.  --The Young Abstract
